---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact - Public Works Digital"
  description="Contact Public Works Digital to discuss how we can help transform your city's technology with open source solutions."
>
  <section class="hero-small">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Let's Build Together</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Ready to transform your city's technology?</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-section">
    <div class="contact-content">
      <div class="contact-intro">
        <p>
          We'd love to hear from you. Whether you're a city official exploring better technology
          solutions, a developer interested in civic tech, or a citizen with questions about
          transparent government technology—reach out and let's start a conversation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

        <div class="contact-method">
          <h3>Email Us</h3>
          <a href="mailto:info@publicworks.digital" class="contact-link">
            info@publicworks.digital
          </a>
          <p class="contact-description">
            For general inquiries, project discussions, or to schedule a consultation
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-types">
          <h3>We're Here to Help With:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Municipal software development projects</li>
            <li>Transitioning from vendor lock-in to open source</li>
            <li>Building transparent citizen engagement platforms</li>
            <li>Modernizing legacy government systems</li>
            <li>Creating sustainable technology strategies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="response-note">
        <p>
          <strong>We typically respond within one business day.</strong> When you reach out,
          please let us know a bit about your organization and what challenges you're facing.
          The more context you provide, the better we can tailor our response to your needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero-small {
    background: var(--gray-50);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  /* Contact Section */
  .contact-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .contact-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-intro p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* Contact Card */
  .contact-card {
    background: var(--gray-50);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-method h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .contact-description {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Contact Types */
  .contact-types {
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-types h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-types ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .contact-types li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  .contact-types li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Response Note */
  .response-note {
    background: #f0f9ff;
    border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .response-note p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .contact-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-link {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero-small {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
